Question 1: What is the name of the config file that has been created after 2020-03-03 and 
is smaller than 28k but larger than 25k?
Solution 1: "find / -type f -name *.conf -size +25k -size -28k -newermt 2020-03-03 2>/dev/null" (This looks for: 
files, with '.conf' in the name, that are greater than 25k, smaller than 28k, creared after 2020-03-03, and sends all
resposnes that say "permission denied" to /dev/null instead of pasting them in the command line,,, respectively)

Question 2: How many files exist on the system that have the ".bak" extension?
Solution 2: "find / -type f -name *.bak 2>/dev/null"

Question 3: Submit the full path of the "xxd" binary.
Solution 3: "find / -type f -name xxd 2>/dev/null"
